---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/+$/, '');
---

<Base title="Andrew Yang — Backend Engineer">
  <h1>Backend engineer who owns data pipelines end-to-end.</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    From vendor API ingestion through message queues to KPI calculation services —
    and everything that repeats gets automated. Three years as the de-facto owner
    of a solar-monitoring ingest pipeline (Kotlin · PHP · RabbitMQ · MySQL · Kubernetes).
  </p>

  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat"><span class="n">3 yrs</span><span class="d">ingest-pipeline de-facto owner, cross-stack root-cause work</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="n">6+</span><span class="d">third-party vendor APIs onboarded end-to-end, each across 6 repositories</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="n">925 → 151 req/s</span><span class="d">hot-path request count −84% — then re-scoped with service-time analysis</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="n">471</span><span class="d">tickets resolved in 3 years, volume doubling year over year</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="n">1,477</span><span class="d">repos in a personal knowledge platform under automated governance</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cards">
    <a class="card" href={`${base}/work/`}>
      <h3>Case studies</h3>
      <p>Six production stories: a site-wide outage turned into the right metric, a million-datapoint export queue-ified, a broker upgrade pre-empted.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href={`${base}/platform/`}>
      <h3>Knowledge platform</h3>
      <p>1,477 repositories, one owner: fleet governance with convention plugins, automated dependency policy, and an AI-assisted content pipeline.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href={`${base}/demo/`}>
      <h3>Live demo — ai-radar</h3>
      <p>A RabbitMQ pipeline with idempotent consumers, a TTL+DLX retry ladder, DLQ replay tooling, and an LLM cost circuit breaker. Running now.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href={`${base}/about/`}>
      <h3>About</h3>
      <p>Background, technical range, and how to reach me.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</Base>
